longBusinessSummary: Thomasville Bancshares, Inc. operates as a bank holding company for Thomasville National Bank that offers various banking products and services. It offers checking and savings account; and loan products comprising mortgages, and consumer and commercial loans, as well as wealth management and mobile banking services. The company was incorporated in 1995 and is based in Thomasville, Georgia.
